}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The '751110-001' ''model'' is found on the sticker affixed to the top of the card used to populate this entry. :A PB code (703875-004) and a MP code (710065-004) is etched onto the bottom of the card.
This device is using an ('''[[Intel]]''' branded) '''Digital Equipment Corporation (DEC)''' 21152-AB PCI bridge.
The device presents itself to the host system as... *One 1011:0024 device (DECchip 21152) *Two 8086:1229 (8086:10f0) devices
